data.description: Charming 2-Story End-Unit Condo Awaiting Your Arrival! Discover this unique treasure located in the heart of the coveted ABC School District. The front yard offers a picturesque park view, bringing nature right to your doorstep. Dive into the magnetic allure of this 2-bedroom townhome, showcasing a bright, recently renovated interior and a prime location. The moment you enter, you're embraced by a pristine aura emanating from every nook. Freshly adorned with upgrades and a new coat of paint, this home resonates with rejuvenation. The kitchen stands out as an epitome of elegance, blending both beauty and utility. As you venture to the second floor, the brand new laminate flooring infuses a contemporary flair. The revamped bathroom boasts new floor tiles, amplifying the aura of sophistication. Step out to enjoy your private covered patio and garden, a quiet haven for relaxation. The spacious Storage Room guarantees ample room for storage, complemented by the additional storage cabinet by the carport for added convenience. Set on a tranquil street, this complex is a quiet sanctuary from daily hustle, yet with swift access to the 91 Freeway, ensuring effortless commuting.
